      <title>参议院共和党因移民冲突阻止向乌克兰提供 660 亿美元援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/ukraine-aid-blocked-by-senate-republicans-over-immigration-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院共和党人阻止了向乌克兰提供 660 亿美元的紧急援助，由于华盛顿在移民政策上持续存在党派僵局，加大了美国对该国战争资金枯竭的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/ukraine-aid-blocked-by-senate-republicans-over-immigration-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 22:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁不顾国际法庭释放前领导人藤森</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/peru-to-free-ex-president-fujimori-defying-international-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁将于周四释放被监禁的前总统阿尔贝托·藤森，这是这个安第斯国家对一个将拉丁美洲所有主要经济体视为成员的国际法庭面临的最严峻的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/peru-to-free-ex-president-fujimori-defying-international-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 22:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将拨款 82 亿美元促进 2024 年关键州的铁路建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/biden-to-award-8-2-billion-boosting-rail-in-key-2024-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登本周将宣布追加 82 亿美元的铁路资金，以推动潜在项目的发展——包括一条通往拉斯维加斯的高速线路—— 2024 年选举的重要州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/biden-to-award-8-2-billion-boosting-rail-in-key-2024-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行高管和立法者在参议院听证会上跳过烟花表演</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-12-06/bank-executives-lawmakers-skip-the-fireworks-at-senate-hearing</link>
