    <item>
      <title>参议员要求对以色列使用美国武器进行更多监督</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/warren-colleagues-press-biden-on-israeli-use-of-us-weapons-in-civilian-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五名民主党参议员敦促拜登政府对以色列使用美国提供的武器进行更多监督，以确保它们不会造成更多平民伤亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/warren-colleagues-press-biden-on-israeli-use-of-us-weapons-in-civilian-deaths</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:41:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>G-7 将于明年开始禁止俄罗斯钻石</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/g-7-moves-to-ban-russian-diamonds-starting-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团同意从明年初起禁止进口俄罗斯钻石，这是遏制俄罗斯资助其入侵乌克兰的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/g-7-moves-to-ban-russian-diamonds-starting-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:08:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大将通过限额与交易制度遏制石油和天然气排放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/canada-to-curb-oil-and-gas-emissions-with-cap-and-trade-regime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大计划利用限额与交易制度限制该国石油和天然气行业的排放，这一政策将成为总理贾斯汀·特鲁多帮助遏制全球变暖的基石，并且几乎肯定会遇到西部省份的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/canada-to-curb-oil-and-gas-emissions-with-cap-and-trade-regime</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 19:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因争取卢旺达妥协而失去移民部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/uk-s-cleverly-says-immigration-minister-jenrick-has-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国移民部长因首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)最近提出将寻求庇护者驱逐到卢旺达而辞职，这凸显了人们对反移民计划不足以平息执政党叛乱的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/uk-s-cleverly-says-immigration-minister-jenrick-has-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 19:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国以1971年以来最强烈举措加强加沙停火呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/un-chief-steps-up-pressure-for-gaza-cease-fire-with-rare-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯戏剧性地升级了对加沙地带停火的呼吁，这是五年来首次使用秘书长可以使用的最有力的工具，这促使安理会成员采取新的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/un-chief-steps-up-pressure-for-gaza-cease-fire-with-rare-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 18:45:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京罕见会见沙特王储以加强两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/putin-meets-uae-ruler-on-rare-trip-to-shore-up-gulf-oil-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在对海湾地区进行的罕见出访中会见了沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼，此次访问旨在加强伙伴关系，并抵制美国和欧洲在全球舞台上孤立他的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/putin-meets-uae-ruler-on-rare-trip-to-shore-up-gulf-oil-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 12:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
